arm_group.description:
A digitally-based ACT program will be conducted in two half-day workshops via meeting software (e.g. Zoom) consisting of:
mindfulness exercises, for stress reduction and to guide nurses to observe their painful thoughts and feelings that they are attempting to avoid;
ACT-metaphors, to let nurses realize the cost of struggling with psychological distress often create more distress;
experiential exercises, to guide nurses to notice their own experiences in providing nursing care throughout their nursing career and explore any special qualities;
explore the nurses' values with respect to different areas in their lives.
